http://

8
00:00:11,109 --> 00:00:11,225
http://h

9
00:00:11,226 --> 00:00:11,343
http://hi

10
00:00:11,344 --> 00:00:11,460
http://hiq

11
00:00:11,461 --> 00:00:11,578
